力控位控程序切换版
进入docker以后：
cd /mnt/data/dexterous_hands
source /opt/ros/noetic/setup.bash 
source devel/setup.bash
roslaunch xhand_control_ros xhand_control.launch 

看到[ INFO] [1736502420.021493921]: XHand device opened就算成功

第二步：
新开终端，然后依次输入：
sudo docker exec -it 8693e11dfcf8 bash
cd /mnt/data/dexterous_hands
source /opt/ros/noetic/setup.bash & source devel/setup.bash
/usr/bin/python3 /mnt/data/dexterous_hands/scripts/hand_switch_controller.py

看到[INFO] [1736502565.985913]: Resetting the system...就算成功

第三步：
新开终端，然后依次输入：
sudo docker exec -it 8693e11dfcf8 bash
cd /mnt/data/dexterous_hands
source /opt/ros/noetic/setup.bash & source devel/setup.bash
/usr/bin/python3 /mnt/data/dexterous_hands/scripts/avp_send_q.py

